### Add Built-in Slug Field to Payload CMS Collection (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/text.mdx

This TypeScript example demonstrates how to integrate the built-in `slugField` into a Payload CMS collection's field schema. It imports `slugField` and `CollectionConfig` from `payload` and adds `slugField()` directly to the `fields` array of the collection configuration, providing automatic slug generation.

```ts
import { slugField } from 'payload'
import type { CollectionConfig } from 'payload'

export const ExampleCollection: CollectionConfig = {
  // ...
  fields: [
    // ...
    // highlight-line
    slugField(),
    // highlight-line
  ],
}
```

