### Define Custom Client Component Field Label in Payload CMS (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/text.mdx

This TypeScript code defines a custom client component for a Payload CMS field label. It uses the `FieldLabel` component from `@payloadcms/ui` and is marked with `'use client'`, rendering a label based on the provided `field` and `path` props.

```tsx
'use client'
import React from 'react'
import { FieldLabel } from '@payloadcms/ui'
import type { TextFieldLabelClientComponent } from 'payload'

export const CustomTextFieldLabelClient: TextFieldLabelClientComponent = ({
  field,
  path,
}) => {
  return (
    <FieldLabel
      label={field?.label || field?.name}
      path={path}
      required={field?.required}
    />
  )
}
```
